name: JAY K. FRP Pvt. Ltd.
overview:
JAY K. FRP PVT. LTD. has been promoted in 1995 by the qualified and well versed persons of the family. Jay Kay Plastics was existing with a reputation of providing quality moulding compounds and moulded components. Jay Kay has been famous for its Bus Bar Supports.

Products & Services: Polyester Moulding Compound Moulding Facility Head Lamp Reflectors SMC Safety Products Moulding Shop MCCB Components

Application: Dough Moulding Compound products find a wide range of applications varying from Automobile parts to Sophisticated and advanced control panels. A few applications to mention are: Circuit Breakers Distribution boxes Slip Ring Assembly Bus Bar Supports (For Control Panel & Switch gears)

Quality Objective: The top management believes that the quality policy is essential for the company’s success and so they support directly the planning of this policy, they periodically review its suitability to determine if it is appropriate for the defined objectives, they also periodically define measurable targets, consistent with the defined policy, for all the prominent organizational functions.

Our Quality Assurance: Our Company is ISO 9001:2008 Certified to ensure compliance to the High quality standards set by the Company.
